    "body": "When a .py file is augmented by a .pxd one, cythonize won’t recompile the module when only the pxd has changed, or one of its dependencies, which often leads to broken code.\n\nThis doesn’t happen when the base module is a .pyx one.\n\nMigrated from http://trac.cython.org/ticket/874",
